outputs.output_descr:
Interagency, bilateral and international cooperation enhanced in and between the South Caucasus countries, EU member states and other international stakeholders; Facilitation of legal movement of people and cargo across border crossing points, while at the same time maintaining secure borders. Specific objectives:
To enhance strategic border management capacities;
Develop and establish broad Border Control Point level procedures and operations;
Demonstrate the benefits of Integrated Border Monitoring via the implementation of pilot programs;
Deliver equipment for pilot Border Control Points for implementation of Integrated Border Management.;
